        "synopsis": {
            "value": "\"Money Flower\" tells the story of people who are driven by greed.\n\nKang Pil-Joo (Jang Hyuk) grew up at an orphanage, but he now works as a managing director of a legal team at a corporation. He is acknowledged for his intelligence and his exemplary job performance. Some of those that work around him are jealous of him.\n\nNa Mo-Hyun (Park Se-Young) is an environmental activist and a science teacher at a middle school. She is a good listener and laughs a lot. She dreams of a love driven by fate.",
            "source": "asianwiki",
            "source_link": "https://asianwiki.com/Money_Flower"
        },
